put the script on your $HOME/bin 

if you want get it locally 
	
	
if you want install the script in your system just put it on 
	
/usr/local/bin 

**safer ^

or if you prefer 

/usr/bin 

If you want just use the script without installation just do this 

(in the folder which  contains the script ..)

chmod +x golgu-translate ; ./golgu-translate -s -i es -o en -t hola muchacho